/ Grammar for matches:     @ - needed property, ! - bad property
/                          isMovable - if Resource needs to be movable
/                          s%f       - if Resource needs to be greater in size then %f
/                          # - resulting resource:its amount (no spaces); use MATCHED to reference matched resource
/
/ Grammar for other tags:  # - needed instrument, / - needed ingredient,
/                          * - what Resource should possess to satisfy CW on this Aspect
/

-MountainLiving             +mountainLiving

-Incinerate
    &@_can_be_ignited--#Fire:1--#Ash:1
-Bake                                                                        /burns
-Roast                                                                       /burns

-MakingFibre
-Weaving
-MakeClothes
-Chisel

-BuildHouse
    &@hard--s0.5--#House:1
-MakeDish
    &@hard--s0.05--#Dish:1
-MakeDye
    &@_colour--#Dye:1

-Killing                                                                     #weapon
-PlantSeed
-TakeApart
-Take
    &!gas--isMovable--#MATCHED:1

-ShapeMalleable                                                              *malleable          #MEANING
-Engrave                                                                     *goodForEngraving   #MEANING
-Carve                                                                       *goodForEngraving   #MEANING
-Paint                                                     *solid        #colour                 #MEANING
-Incrust                                                   *hard         /hard                   #MEANING